"      wMaxPacketSize=49, nframes=6, buffer size=294\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/advanced-networking/_index.adoc:908
msgid ""
"To start and stop the Bluetooth stack, use its startup script. It is a good "
